<h1> App Description </h1>
<p>This is an application for users to ask and answer questions. 
This app provides user <a href="/auth/register">register</a>  and <a href="/auth/login">login</a> functionalities, only logined users can ask or answer questions. 
Users can create their own questions and add answer options with correctness. A question can have multiple correct answers. 
Users can answer random questions in "Quiz" by choosing one option, and then will be shown the results. 
Users can also view the statistics of their own questions and answers, as well as a rank for top 5 users with most correct answers.</p>
